15896 /******************************************************************************/
15897 /* For a painless codes migration between the STM32F4xx device product */
15898 /* lines, the aliases defined below are put in place to overcome the */
15899 /* differences in the interrupt handlers and IRQn definitions. */
15900 /* No need to update developed interrupt code when moving across */
15901 /* product lines within the same STM32F4 Family */
15902 /******************************************************************************/
15903 /* Aliases for __IRQn */
15904 #define FSMC_IRQn FMC_IRQn
15905 
15906 /* Aliases for __IRQHandler */
15907 #define FSMC_IRQHandler FMC_IRQHandler
15908 #define QuadSPI_IRQHandler QUADSPI_IRQHandler
